    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VETITUM_VRC is a horror video game that emulates the experience of watching a VHS that was stored in the police department some years ago, the images that you will see during your investigation were recorded by someone called “Paul Nomdedeu”.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/752749d293deee52b01e3034ec06637c.avif?t=1762059484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras_big/752749d293deee52b01e3034ec06637c.avif?t=1762059484 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All seen from a first person perspective, you will have to investigate every detail of the video tapes to find the truth about this mysterious case about the incident caused in Flemmywoods Park, while it seems that someone is looking for you... <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/3a2ce9313a62a72162cbdbb60c36692e.avif?t=1762059484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras_big/3a2ce9313a62a72162cbdbb60c36692e.avif?t=1762059484 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be very careful </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This contains:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Several Endings? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several hidden endings, a short duration, find the final ending. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you will be able to discover it... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure it doesn't affect you <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/b7890eddb94aa47c173de5779a6b2947.avif?t=1762059484\" width=134 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BEFORE YOU BUY: This game usually lasts 20 minutes if you play it like this, the main mechanic of the game is the research you have to do to the videotape, the length of the game will depend on how long it takes to reach all the endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/3b6b5828a456f7efd8a9894454f7e7ea.poster.avif?t=1762059484\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/3b6b5828a456f7efd8a9894454f7e7ea.webm?t=1762059484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182200/extras/3b6b5828a456f7efd8a9894454f7e7ea.mp4?t=1762059484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
